description: The image shows a presentation screen displaying information about "Insights driven video gen-AI." On the screen, there are two AI-generated images. The first image depicts a tank wearing a wizard's hat in a forest setting. The second image shows a small, lit house with a fence in a nighttime forest. A right-pointing arrow is placed between the two images, implying a transformation or progression. Beneath the first image is the text "Best Performing Static," and beneath the second image is "Performance based prompt to Gemini VEO 2." The screen has a grid pattern and is blue, and it appears to be in a presentation setting, possibly on a stage.
